---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SchemaMarkup from "../../components/SchemaMarkup.astro";
import Icon from "../../components/Icon.astro";

// Make this page dynamic via SSR
export const prerender = false;

const publishDate = new Date("October 12 2026");
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "5 min read";

const isPublished = new Date().getTime() >= publishDate.getTime();

---

<BaseLayout
  title="Fall Deep Cleaning: Dust & Spider Webs Guide"
  description={isPublished ? "Fall deep cleaning guide: tackle dust, spider webs & seasonal buildup in your Huntsville, Florence or Nashville home before the holidays arrive. Expert tips." : "Coming Soon: Fall Deep Cleaning: Combating Dust and Spider Webs"}
  noindex={!isPublished}
  ogImage="https://storage.googleapis.com/msgsndr/iKQIBhpKVL2XVPgU7HMd/media/6920802945dc047d65b4ec5d.png"
>
  <SchemaMarkup
    type="article"
    title="Fall Deep Cleaning: Combating Dust and Spider Webs"
    description="Combat seasonal dust and spider webs with our expert fall deep cleaning guide. Learn professional techniques to prepare your home for the cooler months."
    publishDate="October 12 2026"
    author={author}
  />
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#FFA985]/20 text-[#FFA985] rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Deep Cleaning
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Fall Deep Cleaning: Combating Dust and Spider Webs
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          {isPublished ? "Expert Cleaning Guide" : "Coming October 12 2026."}
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-gray-400 mb-8">
          <span>October 12 2026</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By {author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content Toggle based on Published Date -->
  {isPublished ? (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <!-- TODO: REPLACE THIS SECTION WITH YOUR ACTUAL BLOG CONTENT -->
          <h2>How Do You Combat Dust and Spider Webs with Fall Deep Cleaning?</h2>
<p><strong>Fall deep cleaning is essential for eliminating dust and spider webs, particularly in The Shoals & Surrounding Areas. A thorough, systematic approach ensures every nook and cranny is addressed, providing a cleaner, healthier home environment. The Valley Clean Team specializes in delivering precision cleaning that eradicates these common fall nuisances.</strong></p>
<h3>Why Is Fall Deep Cleaning Important?</h3>
<p>As the leaves fall and temperatures drop, your home becomes a haven for dust and spider webs. These seasonal changes can lead to increased allergens and unwanted pests, impacting your indoor air quality.</p>
<p>Regular cleaning often misses hidden areas where dust and webs accumulate. Deep cleaning addresses these spots, ensuring your home is not only clean but also protected from potential health risks.</p>
<h4>Key Areas to Focus On</h4>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Ceilings and Corners:</strong> Spider webs love high corners and ceilings. A thorough sweep ensures they don't make a comeback.</li>
  <li><strong>Baseboards and Vents:</strong> Dust accumulates quickly in these areas, affecting air quality. Our cleaning specialists ensure they're spotless.</li>
  <li><strong>Behind Furniture:</strong> Hidden dust bunnies can be problematic. We move furniture to guarantee a comprehensive clean.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Our Systematic Approach to Deep Cleaning</h3>
<p>With our military-precision checklists, The Valley Clean Team ensures no detail is overlooked. Here's how we combat dust and spider webs efficiently:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Preparation:</strong> We begin with a detailed assessment of your home to identify critical areas needing attention.</li>
  <li><strong>Advanced Tools:</strong> Using high-efficiency vacuums and dusters, we capture and eliminate dust and webs at the source.</li>
  <li><strong>Expert Techniques:</strong> Our trained cleaning specialists follow proven methods to ensure every surface is meticulously cleaned.</li>
</ul>
<p>Our local expertise in The Shoals & Surrounding Areas means we understand the unique challenges homes face here. We tailor our services to meet these specific needs, guaranteeing satisfaction.</p>
<h3>Benefits of Choosing The Valley Clean Team</h3>
<p>Why should you trust us with your fall deep cleaning?</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Veteran and Women-Owned:</strong> Our disciplined approach ensures accountability and integrity in every clean.</li>
  <li><strong>Transparent Pricing:</strong> Starting at $125, our services are an investment in your home's health and cleanliness.</li>
  <li><strong>Guaranteed Results:</strong> We promise a perfect clean, every time, backed by a 100% satisfaction guarantee.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Reclaim Your Time This Fall</h3>
<p>Stop worrying about dust and spider webs taking over your home. The Valley Clean Team is ready to deliver a spotless, rejuvenated space tailored to your needs. Reclaim your time and enjoy a cleaner, healthier home environment.</p>
<p><strong>Book your guaranteed deep clean today with The Valley Clean Team and experience the precision and professionalism our clients in The Shoals & Surrounding Areas have come to trust.</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  ) : (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white border-t border-gray-100 shadow-inner">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center">
          <Icon name="clock" class="w-16 h-16 text-[#FFA985] mx-auto mb-6" />
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-0">Article Coming Soon!</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 m-0">This article is locked and scheduled to automatically publish on <br/><strong class="text-gray-800 text-xl">October 12 2026</strong>.<br/>Check back then!</p>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition shadow-md no-underline">
              Back to Blog
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  )}
</BaseLayout>
